---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Prose from '../components/Prose.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Botbussen" description="Learn more about Botbussen and our mission to improve clinical skills">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-peach-cream py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Prose>
          <h1 class="text-gradient-full">About Botbussen</h1>
          
          <p>Welcome to Botbussen, a platform dedicated to improving clinical skills and providing inspiration about musculoskeletal health, pain management, and clinical reasoning.</p>
          
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          
          <p>Botbussen aims to bridge the gap between clinical practice and evidence-based knowledge in the field of musculoskeletal health. We focus on:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Clinical Skills Development</strong> - Practical approaches to improving patient assessment and treatment</li>
            <li><strong>Musculoskeletal Health</strong> - In-depth exploration of movement, pain, and rehabilitation</li>
            <li><strong>Pain Management</strong> - Evidence-based strategies for understanding and managing pain</li>
            <li><strong>Clinical Reasoning</strong> - Developing critical thinking skills for better patient outcomes</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
          
          <p>Our content is designed for healthcare professionals, students, and anyone interested in advancing their understanding of musculoskeletal health. You'll discover:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Evidence-Based Articles</strong> - Latest research and clinical insights</li>
            <li><strong>Case Studies</strong> - Real-world examples of clinical reasoning in action</li>
            <li><strong>Practical Guidelines</strong> - Step-by-step approaches to common clinical scenarios</li>
            <li><strong>Educational Resources</strong> - Tools and techniques for skill development</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>Our Approach</h2>
          
          <p>At Botbussen, we believe in the power of continuous learning and evidence-based practice. Our content is carefully curated to provide:</p>
          
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Evidence-Based Information</strong> - All content is grounded in current research and clinical best practices</li>
            <li><strong>Practical Application</strong> - Focus on actionable insights you can implement in your practice</li>
            <li><strong>Professional Development</strong> - Resources to enhance your clinical reasoning and skills</li>
            <li><strong>Community Learning</strong> - A platform for sharing knowledge and experiences</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p>The platform features accessible content, clean typography, and a mobile-first design approach to ensure you can access valuable information wherever you are.</p>
          
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          
          <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have questions about our content, suggestions for future articles, or want to share your clinical experiences, feel free to reach out.</p>
          
          <p>Thank you for visiting Botbussen, and we hope you find valuable insights to enhance your clinical practice!</p>
      </Prose>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
